name: Reddish
body:
### Welcome to the Reddish Project.
A self-hosted version of reddish, a redis visual admin. Use it to inspect and monitor your redis instances.

Install
-------

`npm install -g reddish`

Run
---

`reddish`

### Authors and Contributors
Jim Fleming (@jimfleming) and Danielle Swank (@danielleswank)

### Support or Contact
